{
    "name": "non-blocking-ai",
    "version": "1.0.0",
    "description": "A non-blocking, event-driven AI agent built with Node.js and Google Gemini. Unlike standard chatbots that freeze while \"thinking\" or running tools, this agent uses an Asynchronous Orchestrator. It allows the user to keep chatting while the AI performs long-running tasks (like triggering remote jobs or generating reports) in the background.",
